 class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\"># 잔액 입력</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">while</span> x <span class=\"token operator\">>=</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">print</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>x<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n        x <span class=\"token operator\">-=</span> <span class=\"token number\">1350</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>위 코드는 잔액이 1,350원 미만일 경우를 다루지 못함. 또한 x값 반환보다 print를 먼저 하므로 최종 사용 금액이 나오지 않음.</p>\n<h3 id=\"정답\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%A0%95%EB%8B%B5\" aria-label=\"정답 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>정답</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"python\"><pre class=\"language-python\"><code class=\"language-python\">x <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token builtin\">int</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token builtin\">input</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">while</span> x <span class=\"token operator\">>=</span> <span class=\"token number\">1350</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n    x <span class=\"token operator\">-=</span> <span class=\"token number\">1350</span>\n        <span class=\"token keyword\">print</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>x<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"출력-화면\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%B6%9C%EB%A0%A5-%ED%99%94%EB%A9%B4\" aria-label=\"출력 화면 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>출력 화면</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>잔액이 1,350원일 때</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"python\"><pre class=\"language-python\"><code class=\"language-python\"><span class=\"token number\">1350</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>입력<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token number\">1350</span>\n<span class=\"token number\">0</span></code></pre></div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>잔액이 5,000원일 때</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"python\"><pre class=\"language-python\"><code class=\"language-python\"><span class=\"token number\">5000</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>입력<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token number\">5000</span>\n<span class=\"token number\">3650</span>\n<span class=\"token number\">2300</span>\n<span class=\"token number\">950</span></code></pre></div>\n</li>\n</ul>","fields":{"slug":"/posts/til16","tagSlugs":["/tag/til/","/tag/python/","/tag/코딩도장/","/tag/algorithm/"]},"frontmatter":{"date":"2020-05-07T11:35:32","description":"파이썬 알고리즘 퀴즈","tags":["til","python","코딩도장","algorithm"],"title":"Python - while 반복문으로 교통카드 잔액 출력하기","socialImage":"/naon.png"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/posts/til16"}}}